==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: See blood with one (prick of the) needle.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī zhēn jiàn xiě

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[针]][[见]][[血]]'''

# [[hit the nail on the head]].

===Alternate forms===
[[一針見血]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

